### Get All Customers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers

### Add Customer 1
POST http://localhost:8080/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "john_doe",
  "password": "pass123",
  "email": "john@email.com",
  "licenseNumber": "LIC-001"
}

